<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201104/09e47bebba0a4e81908af8feb263a6e7.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201104/a3b9a5684bf74b59bcea1c87cccc9dee.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201104/c7f41f2fd4eb4983980ef13657cdc36e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201104/e85b211d03ec4a1288349ca0dff0c512.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201104/fdaedc0e86164e9baa16aac175839ac0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201104/505cb861a292494e90ce4dc74c049647.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>深秋西安，秋风给都市染上黄金甲，而浐灞湿地那一幅幅自然画境，给漫步走过留下秋的赞美，也在心中镌刻了对西安秋的那一幅幅美幻画意。</p>
<p>图文：辛秋平</p>